→ VPC endpoints allow you to connect to AWS services privately instead of public internet 

+ VPC endpoints are redundant and horizontally scale 
+ They remove the need of a NAT Gateway , Internet Gateway to access AWS resources 

– in case of issues check DNS settings resolution in your vac 
